<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Tooltician — English / Español</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Choose the English or Spanish version of Tooltician, Carlos Ortega's Python automation consulting site." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://tooltician.com/" />
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="es" href="https://tooltician.com/es/" />
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://tooltician.com/en/" />
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="x-default" href="https://tooltician.com/" />
  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Tooltician — English / Español" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Choose the English or Spanish version of Tooltician, Carlos Ortega's Python automation consulting site." />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://tooltician.com/" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://tooltician.com/assets/images/og-card.png" />
  <meta property="og:image:alt" content="Tooltician preview card" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Tooltician — English / Español" />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Choose the English or Spanish version of Tooltician, Carlos Ortega's Python automation consulting site." />
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://tooltician.com/assets/images/og-card.png" />
  <meta name="twitter:image:alt" content="Tooltician preview card" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" sizes="any" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon-32x32.png" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon-16x16.png" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" />
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/apple-touch-icon.png" sizes="180x180" />
  <style>
    :root {
      color-scheme: dark;
      --bg: #070d1a;
      --surface: #0f1729;
      --surface-2: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
      --text: #e8eaf6;
      --muted: #98a3b8;
      --accent: #6c63ff;
      --accent-2: #00d4aa;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.18), transparent 40%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #0c1426 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .gateway {
      width: min(100%, 920px);
      padding: 2rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 28px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02)),
        var(--surface);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .gateway__logo {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .gateway__eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .gateway__title {
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      font-family: "Space Grotesk", "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.4rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .gateway__copy {
      margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
      max-width: 44rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .gateway__options {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .gateway__card {
      display: block;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: var(--surface-2);
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform 150ms ease, border-color 150ms ease, background 150ms ease;
    }

    .gateway__card:hover,
    .gateway__card:focus-visible {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      border-color: rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.45);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
      outline: none;
    }

    .gateway__card strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }

    .gateway__card span {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .gateway__note {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .gateway {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 24px;
      }

      .gateway__options {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="gateway">
    <img class="gateway__logo" src="/assets/images/tooltician-logo-128.webp" alt="" width="64" height="64" decoding="async">
    <p class="gateway__eyebrow">Tooltician · Carlos Ortega Gonzalez</p>
    <h1 class="gateway__title">Choose your language</h1>
    <p class="gateway__copy">Python automation consulting for reporting, ETL, internal tools, and workflows that need to keep working after handoff.</p>

    <div class="gateway__options">
      <a class="gateway__card" href="/en/">
        <strong>English</strong>
        <span>Production-focused portfolio, public proof, and a direct project brief.</span>
      </a>
      <a class="gateway__card" href="/es/">
        <strong>Español</strong>
        <span>Portafolio orientado a producción, evidencia pública y brief de proyecto directo.</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="gateway__note">Both versions are maintained and link to the same public work, packages, and contact paths.</p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
